OL,6,FFive men have been convicted for their
OL,7,Frole in the sexual exploitation of
OL,8,Fyoung girls in Gateshead.
OL,10,FCodrin Dura, 27, Leonard Paun, 23,
OL,11,FBogdan Guguiman, 44, Klaudio Aleksiu,
OL,12,F28 and Stefan Ciuraru, 22, were each
OL,13,Ffound guilty on Tuesday (14 October)
OL,14,Fof offences relating to the sexual
OL,15,Fexploitation of six girls in the
OL,16,FGateshead area between March 2015 and
OL,17,FMay 2019.
