OL,6,F"For some of the victims, what began
OL,7,Fas a relationship with one person
OL,8,Fdescended into them being passed
OL,9,Fbetween group members, where they were
OL,10,Froutinely abused while heavily
OL,11,Fintoxicated.
OL,13,F"The Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,14,Fworked closely with Northumbria Police
OL,15,Fto build a robust case against these
OL,16,Fmen. Their abuse of these girls has
OL,17,Fhad a lasting and traumatic effect
OL,18,Fupon them, which continues to impact
OL,19,Fon their mental and emotional
OL,20,Fwellbeing into their adult life.
